((MW2*Nc*cTAG[Yuk]^2*DiagMark[MT, MB]*(-(CB2*hb^2*Re[B0[0, 0, MB2]]) - 
     ht^2*SB2*Re[B0[0, MB2, MT2]] - (ht^2*SB2*Re[B0[0, 0, MT2]] + 
       2*CB2*hb^2*Re[B0[0, MB2, MT2]] + (CB2*hb^2 - ht^2*SB2)*
        Re[B1[0, MB2, MT2]])/(-3 + 2*del)))/(8*Pi^2) + 
  (Alfa*Nc*SumOver[Sfe3, 2]*(DiagMark[MSf[Sfe3, 4, 3]]*MSf2[Sfe3, 4, 3]*
      Re[B0[0, 0, MSf2[Sfe3, 4, 3]]]*UCSf[Sfe3, 1, 4, 3] + 
     UCSf[Sfe3, 1, 3, 3]*(DiagMark[MSf[Sfe3, 3, 3]]*MSf2[Sfe3, 3, 3]*
        Re[B0[0, 0, MSf2[Sfe3, 3, 3]]] + 
       (2*DiagMark[MSf[Sfe3, 3, 3], MSf[Sfe4, 4, 3]]*
         (MSf2[Sfe4, 4, 3]*Re[B0[0, 0, MSf2[Sfe4, 4, 3]]] + 
          2*MSf2[Sfe3, 3, 3]*Re[B0[0, MSf2[Sfe3, 3, 3], MSf2[Sfe4, 4, 3]]] + 
          (MSf2[Sfe3, 3, 3] - MSf2[Sfe4, 4, 3])*Re[B1[0, MSf2[Sfe3, 3, 3], 
             MSf2[Sfe4, 4, 3]]])*SumOver[Sfe4, 2]*UCSf[Sfe4, 1, 4, 3])/
        (-3 + 2*del))))/(8*Pi*SW2))/MW2
